'''
PRACTICE WRITING (APPENDING) TO EXCEL SHEET WITHOUT USING EXCEL WRITER;
This should use the function, open. Therefore, it keys all the current Excel formulas within the Excel sheet.
Using  df = pd.read_excel(file)  and  df.to_excel(writer,'Sheet1', index=False)  will NOT carry over Excel formulas.
#https://stackoverflow.com/questions/58160030/how-to-read-xlsx-as-pandas-dataframe-with-formulas-as-strings
'''

